OL,5, Around 24,000 staff at British Airways 
OL,6, will get a pay rise worth more than 13%
OL,7, over 18 months from September, the     
OL,8, Unite union has said.                  
OL,10,FWorkers will also get a one-off payment
OL,11,Fof #1,000, but pilots and management   
OL,12,Fare excluded from the deal, it said.   
OL,14,FThe deal, after months of negotiations,
OL,15,Feases the threat of disruption as      
OL,16,Fdemand for air travel soars.           
OL,18,FWorkers are pushing for higher pay in a
OL,19,Fnumber of sectors as inflation         
OL,20,Fcontinues to be high.                  
